	* src/debug.h, src/ring.h: Use G_BEGIN_DECLS/G_END_DECLS.
	* src/reaper.h: Use G_BEGIN_DECLS/G_END_DECLS in the right place.
	* src/vteapp.c: Add -B/-T flags to set background images and
	transparency.
